                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Peculia<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>ri</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> COD <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>discent</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>onendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Rechteckstele mit eingeschriebenem Dreiecksgiebel mit Akroteren, im Giebelfeld Lunette. Unten abgebrochen. Z. 4: NT-Ligatur. (B): Z. 2-4: Joly: Peculia/ri(s) Codi (filii?) / Discent(es eius); Le Bohec: Peculia/ri Cod(oni) (filio) / Discent(es eius).</p>
            </div>
